        "TileImage": "$($repository 5c309d9c-a738-4d83-898c-e427e6f67d9a).Image",
        "Description": "Good Afternoon 47. Your target today is Kate Switzer. A well-known con artist in the art world who targets unsuspecting buyers by selling well made fake art pieces. Our client was one of these unsuspecting buyers and has decided the law cannot help them with this matter. We have intel that Kate is on vacation in Miami with her boyfriend and loves to run around the coast. Use whatever means necessary 47, but remember to leave no traces. \r\rGood Luck 47.",
